title: Jersey Mike’s Is Working With Morgan Stanley, JPMorgan on IPO
description: Jersey Mike’s Subs, the sandwich chain with more than 3,000 locations, is working with Morgan Stanley, JPMorgan Chase & Co., and Jefferies Financial Group Inc. on an initial public offering, according to people familiar with the matter.
